articles.author: Amani Bayo
articles.title: ‘Free America Walkout’ brings protesters to downtown Columbus in bitter cold - dispatch.com
articles.description: Roughly 150 demonstrators gathered at 2 p.m. Jan. 20 as part of a nationwide protest marking the anniversary of President Trump’s inauguration.
articles.content:
• Demonstrators are planning a nationwide "Free America Walkout" to protest the policies of the Trump administration.
